The data has been downloaded in May 2021 from:

https://ftp.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pub/COG/COG2020/data/

The website lists available data as well as related publications.


translation table is split in subparts to keep the files small.

run
cat cog-20.translation_cog* >> cog-20.all-translation.tsv
to collect single files into one.